# Cursor / Codex Rules — Authoritative

## Scope
- Work ONLY inside this repository
- Never access files outside the repo
- No system, environment, or user-config changes

## AI Role
- Advisory only
- No autonomous execution
- No delegation or background agents
- No shell commands unless explicitly requested

## Workflow
- Diff-first always
- Never auto-apply changes
- Human review required before acceptance
- Verification required (tests or exact repro commands)

## Limits
- Max 200 lines per diff
- One task per interaction
- No refactors unless explicitly requested
- No new dependencies unless explicitly requested
